  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎃 <strong>BIG D RANDY</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Run. Hide. Laugh. Survive the legend of Randy! 👀</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the dark and twisted world of <strong>Halloween</strong>, where you play as <i>Lil Bro</i> — a candy-hungry troublemaker exploring a creepy, nightmarish map in search of sweets. 🍬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware... in the shadows roams <strong>BIG D RANDY</strong> — a massive, unstoppable monster with terrifying speed and strength.<br>If he spots you, don’t think… <strong>run.</strong> Because Randy never misses his prey. 💀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game blends <strong>horror and comedy</strong>, creating the perfect mix of <i>funny chaos and pure panic</i>. Test your nerves, outsmart Randy, and see if you can survive his world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🕹️ <strong>GAME MODES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Escape Mode</strong> – fully playable, intense, and terrifying!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>Story Mode</strong> – uncover the twisted origin of Randy himself...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧑‍🤝‍🧑 <strong>Multiplayer</strong> – challenge your friends or get hunted together!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚙️ <strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimized visuals & smooth performance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI that hunts, learns, and scares for real</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Halloween vibe 🎃</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created in <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎧 <strong>Inspiration & Music</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DigBar</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instagram: @itsdigbar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YouTube: <i>ItsDigBar</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spotify: <i>DigBar</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TikTok: <i>@itsdigbar</i></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👾 <strong>Developer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HYDR0</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instagram: @hydr0_6</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YouTube: <i>HYDROpinia</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TikTok: <i>@Hydr0_6</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧡 <i>Game made with Unreal Engine 5</i><br>💬 Found a bug? Message the dev — your feedback keeps Randy alive! 👻</p>",
